  "text": "A number of studies have shown that terminating the surgical procedure may be beneficial in the patients who are preoperatively suspected with gallbladder cancer and undergo biopsy [CITATION_1] . However, we preferred to continue the surgery since we had no available conditions for frozen biopsy during the surgery and the procedure was completed with no complication.",
